            <p>In addition to my startup background, I'm seeking to understand social issues with data engineering and statistical approaches with my nonprofit projects. Now my goal is to contribute to a better understanding between society and technology. I'm looking forward to be a part of a team that aims to make a next bold move. By utilizing my diverse experiences in both design and engineering, I'd love to collaborate with great teammates in different areas.</p>
